{"tid":2275847,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[DLC] Sony 證實 PS5 出機時未支援擴充 SSD    外置硬碟不能安裝 PS5 遊戲","createTime":"2020-11-07T12:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T18:13:34.000Z","uid":15564,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"b15499b6dd060bce379c033a9ab056318790f971","tid":2275847,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:53:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/sony-%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6-ps5-%E5%87%BA%E6%A9%9F%E6%99%82%E6%9C%AA%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E6%93%B4%E5%85%85-ssd-%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%AE%E7%A1%AC%E7%A2%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D/?amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fsony-%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25AF%25A6-ps5-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%2585%2585-ssd-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E7%25A2%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%259D%2F%3Famp&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuPdVh5kQGr0UM1CkPSjmotI%3D&h=23d71ef3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/sony-%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6-ps5-%E5%87%BA%E6%A9%9F%E6%99%82%E6%9C%AA%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E6%93%B4%E5%85%85-ssd-%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%AE%E7%A1%AC%E7%A2%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D/?amp</a><br />\n<br />\nSony 早前曾發表一條官方拆機影片，可以看到 PS5 主機上有個擴充 SSD 插槽，讓用戶可以自己加裝讀取速度 5.5GB/s 以上的 M.2 介面 NVMe SSD 。不過官方最近就向傳媒證實，大家在發賣首日買到的 PlayStation 5 原來還未可以自行加裝 SSD 擴充，而使用 USB 連接的外置硬碟，也不能用來安裝 PS5 遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://plugmedia-wp-uploads.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Screenshot-2020-10-08-at-01.18.00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplugmedia-wp-uploads.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FScreenshot-2020-10-08-at-01.18.00.jpg&h=6892acd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">這條 M.2 擴充槽在最初仍未有作用，要等待日後軟件更新。</span><br />\n<br />\n揭開 PlayStation 5 主機白色外殼，就會見到支援 PCIe 4.0 的 M.2 SSD 插槽， Sony 曾說過用戶可以購買市販的 M.2 SSD 來擴充主機容量，不過原來這個插槽在推出初期會是無效的， Sony 對傳媒表示要留待將來更新的。<br />\n<br />\n其實這件事早在三月 GDC 時 PlayStation 的硬件工程師 Mark Cerny 早就已經預告了，他當時表示「如果能在上市時實現就太好了，不過這很可能會有點延遲，請暫緩購買 M.2 SSD 直至你收到我們的消息。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://plugmedia-wp-uploads.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Screenshot-2020-11-06-at-23.28.34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplugmedia-wp-uploads.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FScreenshot-2020-11-06-at-23.28.34.jpg&h=c8911c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">早在今年三月，PlayStation 的硬件工程師 Mark Cerny 就曾預告 PlayStation 可能不能在推出初期提供 SSD 擴充功能。</span><br />\n<br />\nMark Cerny 市面上不是所有 M.2 SSD 都夠快跟得上 PS5 的速度、尺寸剛好放入 PS5 的 SSD 擴充槽，或兼容 Sony 的 I/O 控制器， Sony 承諾會在今年稍後進行兼容性測試。他表示 SSD 需要支援 PCIe Gen4 以提供不低於 5.5GB/s 速度，並且沒有很大的散熱片才能裝入 PS5 擴充槽。不過據業內人士透露，這個兼容性測試可能還未展開。<br />\n<br />\nPlayStation 5 剛備 825GB 內置 SSD ，不過據早前流出的資料顯示扣除系統佔用的空間之後， PS5 實際上能使用的空間有 667GB 。<br />\n<br />\n至於外置硬碟的限制，主要是由於 PS5 遊戲都需要超高速載入速度，必須要安裝在內置 SSD 才能實現，所以不能安裝在外置硬碟上。可能 Sony 要為用戶想想辨法盡快提供擴充方案，因為像《 Spider-Man: Miles Morales Ultimate Launch Edition 》就佔用 105GB 容量， PS5 可能只安裝 6 款 AAA 大作內存就會爆滿。"},{"pid":"63b2950c66bb8b7101445976f69711a3d97aabcb","tid":2275847,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c61c8930e4e1bde29c70d8a1ca1565103fe15f","tid":2275847,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:56:24.000Z","msg":"出自家外置SSD<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16a733c5d6bfbc94fe8369ddaf530e9f31cf86e","tid":2275847,"uid":64347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"一定係自家品牌，唔係點賺你錢"},{"pid":"377ea685c598173ea6b4e6cbbedc71782d942896","tid":2275847,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"f16a733c5d6bfbc94fe8369ddaf530e9f31cf86e","tid"